8
00:00:44,122 --> 00:00:45,122
My name is Markus Montola.

9
00:00:45,503 --> 00:00:47,805
I've been working on location-based games for 15

10
00:00:48,305 --> 00:00:48,605
years.

11
00:00:49,626 --> 00:00:52,528
In 2009, we wrote a book and published a book called

