00:21:27,832 --> 00:21:32,374
but you got better loot, and, like, this was a disaster.

321
00:21:32,694 --> 00:21:38,676
So players immediately lost immersion when they saw the 2D map versus actually the, like, the map they projected you.

322
00:21:40,436 --> 00:21:44,900
And mixing on location play and the 2D map turned out to be incredibly confusing.

323
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:47,602
So vast majority of people kind of like not only lost immersion,

324
00:21:48,023 --> 00:21:50,705
they couldn't quite figure out where they were, where the heroes were,

