00:21:50,725 --> 00:21:53,908
and like they just like lost, like they just couldn't cope with them

326
00:21:53,928 --> 00:21:55,069
with the information they were seeing.

327
00:21:56,030 --> 00:21:58,932
So we figured, okay, like this is going to be way too complicated for a loop

328
00:21:59,112 --> 00:22:00,593
and we just decided to kill this.

