00:22:20,195 --> 00:22:24,939
And again, like completely disastrous results were way too complicated to be the core loop activity.

332
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:30,064
And also secondly, like this felt psychologically wrong where we have this mental model of the

333
00:22:30,104 --> 00:22:35,588
world where we kind of think where the natural boundaries of areas lie. And the people are like

334
00:22:35,769 --> 00:22:41,874
really objected to us splitting the world into areas that didn't really correlate with anything

